# ─── Delhi City Dashboard — API keys ────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to ".env.local" and fill in the values you have.
# The air-quality and weather panels work with NO keys at all.
# Add these two keys to light up the live bus and events panels.

# 1) Delhi Open Transit Data (live bus GPS, GTFS-Realtime)
#    Register free at: https://otd.delhi.gov.in  -> "Register" -> get an API key.
OTD_API_KEY=

# 2) Real-Time Events Search (RapidAPI) — live Delhi events (Google Events aggregate)
#    Register free at: https://rapidapi.com -> search "Real-Time Events Search"
#    -> Subscribe (Basic/free plan) -> copy the "X-RapidAPI-Key".
RAPIDAPI_KEY=
